Task-2-3_key2:
**Leap Year** har 4 saal me ek baar ahta hai aur woh bi ush saal me joh `4 se divisible hota hai`. Lekin saat hi agar woh saal `100 se divisible hai` magar `400 se divisible nhi hai`.
Toh woh **Leap Year** nhi kehlata hai.
Task-2-3_key3:
Eg:
  1800 **Leap Year** nhi hai kyunki yeh `100 se divisible hai` magar `400 se divisible nhi hai`
  2000 **Leap Year** hai kyunki yeh `100 se divisible hai` aur `400 se divisible hai`
Task-2-3_key5: Apko ish Task me `input` ke torh pe saal diya jayega aur apko ush saal ke 3 pichle **Leap Year** print karne hai.
Task-2-3_key6: Aur Jab 3 pichle **Leap Year** nikal jaye toh uske baad aap 3 ane wale **Leap Year** nikalne hai apko.
Task-2-3_key8: Apne program ko test karne ke liye ish `input` ko dale ke uske `output` check kare
Task-2-3_key10: Aap 3 leap year (aage yeah pichle wale) aye usko pata karne k liye ek alag varibale rakh sakte ho.Joh apki madad karega yeh jane meh 3 leap year nikal gaye ya nhi.
